description: [``botocore``] Adds GetGateway and UpdateGatewaySoftwareNow API and adds hypervisor name to UpdateHypervisor API
[``botocore``] Added Format field to Import and Export APIs in Amazon Forecast. Added TimeSeriesSelector to Create Forecast API.

[``botocore``] Adds support for centrally controlling each participant's ability to send and receive audio, video and screen share within a WebRTC session.  Attendee capabilities can be specified when the attendee is created and updated during the session with the new BatchUpdateAttendeeCapabilitiesExcept API.
[``botocore``] Add new APIs to support Route 53 IP Based Routing
